block_trips_with_overlapping_stop_times.description: Describes two trips with the same block id that have overlapping stop times.

csvRowNumberA.description: The row number from `trips.txt` of the first faulty trip.

csv_parsing_failed.description:
Parsing of a CSV file failed.

One common case of the problem is when a cell value contains more than 4096 characters.

foreign_key_violation.description:
The values of the given key and rows of one table cannot be found a values of the given key in
another table.

This is the case when a foreign key of one table references a non-existing value in its
original table.
